Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.62,Default,Czesla,0,0,0,,Ehmm, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの… 大丈夫ですか?
